259
00:12:30.501 --> 00:12:33.420
- Yeah.
- That's quite the memory there. Sonequa.

260
00:12:33.504 --> 00:12:34.713
- I know!
- Oh. yeah!

261
00:12:34.797 --> 00:12:36.215
Yeah. that's... that's impressive.

262
00:12:36.298 --> 00:12:37.466
That's impressive.

263
00:12:38.926 --> 00:12:41.595
Tunde. I remember
there was a conversation we had on set.

264
00:12:41.679 --> 00:12:43.722
and I remember...

265
00:12:43.806 --> 00:12:47.351
So. for those of you who may not know.
