270
00:13:01.490 --> 00:13:03.492
with always wanting to elevate
the standard.

271
00:13:03.575 --> 00:13:06.203
I was just speaking about Eve coming
on the show and Elias.

272
00:13:06.745 --> 00:13:08.205
They're surrounded by people

273
00:13:08.288 --> 00:13:12.751
who are actively pursuing elevation.
innovation. and working hard.

274
00:13:12.835 --> 00:13:15.337
And I love how we celebrate that.
champion that.

275
00:13:15.421 --> 00:13:19.216
