to do the best that we can.

276
00:13:19.299 --> 00:13:21.802
I think it's something
that's really inspired me.

277
00:13:21.885 --> 00:13:24.722
I love the way Tunde
never shied away from that. truly.

278
00:13:24.805 --> 00:13:25.805
Oh. yeah.

279
00:13:25.848 --> 00:13:26.849
Thanks for that.

280
00:13:30.185 --> 00:13:33.063
It's hard. what we do.
and our audience is very demanding.

281
00:13:33.147 --> 00:13:35.691
you know. and they...

282
00:13:38.402 --> 00:13:41.780
