295
00:14:26.658 --> 00:14:29.244
There are no words.
There are not enough words.

296
00:14:33.207 --> 00:14:34.249
That's true.

297
00:14:35.292 --> 00:14:37.461
That's true. My gratitude knows no bounds.

298
00:14:37.544 --> 00:14:39.296
I know we all feel the same.

