00:14:41.715 --> 00:14:44.510
Our first...
The first week out with us. David.

301
00:14:45.719 --> 00:14:48.722
- Oh. Lord. I'm still recovering.
- Yes.

302
00:14:48.806 --> 00:14:49.973
I'm still recovering.

303
00:14:51.391 --> 00:14:52.684
You put me through it.

304
00:14:52.768 --> 00:14:56.605
You played it down when you introduced
the idea of being in Iceland

