00:15:00.651 --> 00:15:01.985
I went through everything.

307
00:15:04.071 --> 00:15:05.989
Jumped off of a cliff with SMG...

308
00:15:06.949 --> 00:15:07.950
Yeah!

309
00:15:08.617 --> 00:15:11.620
- In the hot springs.
