00:15:19.169 --> 00:15:20.462
I remember that.

314
00:15:20.546 --> 00:15:21.755
That's amazing.

315
00:15:21.839 --> 00:15:23.841
You know. I gotta send it to you.
you know.

316
00:15:24.508 --> 00:15:25.509
Please.

