326
00:15:49.658 --> 00:15:50.742
Yeah. exactly.

327
00:15:51.702 --> 00:15:52.744
Yeah.

328
00:15:52.828 --> 00:15:56.832
And the color of this. Tunde.
this was done in-camera. wasn't it?

