- Wow.

334
00:16:13.098 --> 00:16:15.350
And that sequence was fascinating

335
00:16:15.434 --> 00:16:17.245
because we actually shot it
in two and a half hours.

336
00:16:17.269 --> 00:16:18.729
the infrared sequence.

337
00:16:19.605 --> 00:16:24.693
And. you know. that only happened because
the cast shows up totally rehearsed.

338
00:16:24.776 --> 00:16:26.403
