339
00:16:26.486 --> 00:16:29.281
Stunt players show up totally rehearsed.
ready to go.

340
00:16:29.364 --> 00:16:31.617
And we were a well-oiled machine
at that point.

341
00:16:31.700 --> 00:16:35.245
