365
00:17:40.769 --> 00:17:43.105
in. you know. where they did come in.

366
00:17:43.188 --> 00:17:45.107
Of course. me and Eve did a lot of it.

367
00:17:45.190 --> 00:17:48.902
But they did an amazing job
with what they did do.

368
00:17:51.363 --> 00:17:53.615
And yeah. we were all. again.

369
00:17:53.699 --> 00:17:56.868
