372
00:18:04.334 --> 00:18:07.379
But it's like you said. Tunde.
we really challenged ourselves.

373
00:18:08.005 --> 00:18:10.465
and we put all of our. you know.

374
00:18:10.549 --> 00:18:14.678
collective knowledge
and skill and experience together

375
00:18:14.761 --> 00:18:19.766
