"Let's go higher. Let's go further.

376
00:18:20.684 --> 00:18:24.438
Let's reach."
And we did. and then we did it.

377
00:18:24.521 --> 00:18:26.315
We ended up doing it.

378
00:18:27.816 --> 00:18:30.402
One of the things I love most
about this entire team

379
00:18:30.485 --> 00:18:34.656
is that there's never a time
where something is presented

380
00:18:34.740 --> 00:18:39.036
