I'm noticing what the camera is doing...

434
00:21:32.417 --> 00:21:33.877
and it kind of pulls me out.

435
00:21:33.960 --> 00:21:37.964
And so. one of the things
I love about you and the way you direct

436
00:21:38.048 --> 00:21:40.175
and this team
and all the directors that we have

437
00:21:40.258 --> 00:21:44.554
is that it always feels
of a piece with the story.

438
00:21:44.638 --> 00:21:49.142
And I'm never just kind of
noticing something just to notice it.

439
00:21:49.226 --> 00:21:52.896
It all feels very organic
to what's happening emotionally.

440
00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:55.232
I mean. like. look at this. It's great.

441
00:21:56.149 --> 00:21:57.567
It's so alive.

442
00:21:57.651 --> 00:22:01.696
And I gotta big-up our new bridge.

443
00:22:01.780 --> 00:22:06.409
