444
00:22:06.493 --> 00:22:07.911
because they came in...

445
00:22:08.745 --> 00:22:13.250
they came in. you know. sort of.
or toward the tail end. at least.

446
00:22:13.333 --> 00:22:15.460
And they had a big job ahead of them

447
00:22:15.544 --> 00:22:20.173
to come into this. you know.
fully functioning machine.

448
00:22:20.257 --> 00:22:22.884
This family... Of course.
we welcome them as family.

449
00:22:22.968 --> 00:22:25.053
and they were quickly family.

450
00:22:25.136 --> 00:22:29.432
And they just... they just...
they sank right in.

451
00:22:29.516 --> 00:22:31.184
- did they not?
- Yeah.

452
00:22:32.185 --> 00:22:33.562
It's like they didn't miss a beat.

453
00:22:35.605 --> 00:22:37.774
I was really grateful
for all of them for that.

454
00:22:38.316 --> 00:22:40.277
- Yeah.
- It's no easy thing.

455
00:22:40.360 --> 00:22:42.862
I mean. we're watching it and. you know.
as an audience member.

456
00:22:42.946 --> 00:22:45.282
the bridge is moving and it's shaking
and there's things...

457
00:22:45.365 --> 00:22:46.366
Yes!

458
00:22:46.449 --> 00:22:50.662
But for you guys in the cast.
that's all just... that's camera movement.

459
00:22:50.745 --> 00:22:54.916
But for a new actor coming in.
there are explosions happening.

460
00:22:55.000 --> 00:22:59.337
there's smoke. there's Tunde saying.
"Go... Go left. Go right!"

461
00:23:00.005 --> 00:23:01.423
Right. Exactly.

462
00:23:01.506 --> 00:23:03.508
And out of... just starting off.

463
00:23:03.592 --> 00:23:06.720
