you know. what they're doing

465
00:23:10.307 --> 00:23:13.143
and it's no small task.

466
00:23:13.226 --> 00:23:14.436
That's right.

467
00:23:14.978 --> 00:23:16.730
It's quite a thing to jump into.

468
00:23:16.813 --> 00:23:18.189
And Callum. you know.

469
00:23:19.566 --> 00:23:22.027
