00:35:09.025 --> 00:35:13.154
you're making a point to point out
everyone and their contributions.

706
00:35:15.156 --> 00:35:16.949
And that's just really lovely.

707
00:35:17.033 --> 00:35:18.034
It's one of the...

708
00:35:18.117 --> 00:35:22.705
Like. that generosity of spirit
just in this

709
00:35:22.788 --> 00:35:25.583
and in the way you are
with everybody on set...

710
00:35:25.666 --> 00:35:28.919
you're just honestly a dream to work with.

711
00:35:29.003 --> 00:35:32.882
and we love you.
and I just love that about you.

712
00:35:32.965 --> 00:35:34.300
That's who you are.

713
00:35:35.843 --> 00:35:37.011
Michelle...

714
00:35:37.803 --> 00:35:40.931
Thank you for saying that. Praise God.

715
00:35:41.015 --> 00:35:42.141
That's so...

716
00:35:42.224 --> 00:35:44.226
I think
you're gonna make her cry. Michelle.

717
00:35:44.310 --> 00:35:46.729
I know. Look. I know.

718
00:35:46.812 --> 00:35:49.148
- I do not want to cry.
