1223
01:02:31.415 --> 01:02:32.500
<i>Disco</i> movie.

1224
01:02:34.001 --> 01:02:35.601
Oh. my goodness. that woman right there.

1225
01:02:35.670 --> 01:02:36.837
- Tara.
- Tara.

1226
01:02:36.921 --> 01:02:39.131
