1229
01:02:47.139 --> 01:02:49.684
We. like... We would just marvel at her.

1230
01:02:50.184 --> 01:02:51.185
Absolutely.

1231
01:02:51.268 --> 01:02:56.107
By the way. Tunde and Frakes
