1240
01:03:12.206 --> 01:03:17.128
you know what I'm saying? Like.
man. just. stellar artists and just...

1241
01:03:17.211 --> 01:03:20.756
I love this relationship so much.

1242
01:03:21.465 --> 01:03:23.426
That's such a...
I've told this story before.

