1344
01:08:22.474 --> 01:08:24.852
about the Progenitor
and what Burnham learned.

1345
01:08:24.935 --> 01:08:28.939
And she had a line that she said
to Book about that.

1346
01:08:29.023 --> 01:08:33.193
that we then ultimately put
in the next scene with the son.

1347
01:08:33.277 --> 01:08:34.903
and gave that to her to give to him.

1348
01:08:34.987 --> 01:08:38.866
That was really the only thing
we had to change in this

1349
01:08:39.575 --> 01:08:42.286
to be able to make that work.
But this was gonna be the last shot.

1350
01:08:42.369 --> 01:08:43.370
Yeah.

1351
01:08:43.912 --> 01:08:47.166
Phil. if you're listening to this.
Phil. that was an amazing scene.

1352
01:08:47.249 --> 01:08:49.289
- Oh. my gosh. Yeah. Look at this.
- It's beautiful.

1353
01:08:49.460 --> 01:08:50.919
It's beautiful.

1354
01:08:51.003 --> 01:08:52.755
- And then here we go.
- It's my favorite.

1355
01:08:52.838 --> 01:08:55.632
Here it's gonna be...
You guys are ending the season now.

1356
01:08:55.716 --> 01:08:57.009
What... What...

1357
01:08:57.092 --> 01:08:59.053
I can't watch this. I can't watch this.

1358
01:08:59.136 --> 01:09:01.930
I'm curious... What was it like to look...

1359
01:09:02.014 --> 01:09:03.098
I can't watch it.

1360
01:09:03.182 --> 01:09:04.742
What was it like to look in the mirror?

1361
01:09:04.808 --> 01:09:07.019
What was it like to look in the mirror
with the...

1362
01:09:07.102 --> 01:09:09.188
He walked away! He's gone.

1363
01:09:09.271 --> 01:09:10.647
- Gone.
- He keeps calling us...

1364
01:09:10.731 --> 01:09:14.193
Listen. I'm here. but I can't. I can't.
My heart is too...

1365
01:09:14.276 --> 01:09:15.378
- Oh. no. no. I can't.
- I know.

1366
01:09:15.402 --> 01:09:17.780
- I know. David can't really watch.
- I can't.

1367
01:10:14.378 --> 01:10:18.090
So. I just remember...
I remember seeing my mom

1368
01:10:18.173 --> 01:10:21.051
when I was looking in the mirror
when I was. you know. working.

1369
01:10:21.135 --> 01:10:23.429
It was Nicola and Brandi who...

1370
01:10:23.512 --> 01:10:26.140
You know. we were together
every day doing this.

1371
01:10:26.223 --> 01:10:29.518
I was so grateful to be able
to do this on my way out.

1372
01:10:29.601 --> 01:10:32.980
I felt like the cool kid. and it was so...

1373
01:10:33.939 --> 01:10:36.900
Man. it was so lifelike and true.

1374
01:10:38.068 --> 01:10:41.113
And David and I both.
we just could not have imagined

1375
01:10:41.738 --> 01:10:46.910
a sweeter gift to be given on the way out.

1376
01:10:46.994 --> 01:10:49.496
So. you know.
I will just always be grateful

1377
01:10:49.580 --> 01:10:51.665
to you. Michelle. and everyone.

1378
01:10:51.748 --> 01:10:53.959
And you too. Tunde.
for bringing it to life

1379
01:10:54.042 --> 01:10:56.336
and giving us the opportunity to...

1380
01:10:56.420 --> 01:10:58.088
Oh. my goodness...

1381
01:10:58.172 --> 01:11:02.176
show these people
living happily ever after. basically.

1382
01:11:02.718 --> 01:11:06.930
I will be grateful
to CBS Studios. Paramount+.

1383
01:11:07.014 --> 01:11:08.348
- They. you know...
- Yes.

1384
01:11:08.432 --> 01:11:10.559
...to allow us to do this.

1385
01:11:10.642 --> 01:11:13.479
And. by the way.
as we were prepping for this.

1386
01:11:13.562 --> 01:11:15.564
the writers' strike was coming up.

1387
01:11:15.647 --> 01:11:19.776
And so we knew that
we had to shoot this before May 1st

1388
01:11:19.860 --> 01:11:21.195
because everyone wanted...

1389
01:11:21.278 --> 01:11:23.947
We didn't... No one knew for sure
