to come back and shoot this.

1392
01:11:29.620 --> 01:11:32.206
So I think ultimately...
Tunde. correct me if I'm wrong...

1393
01:11:32.289 --> 01:11:36.084
I think we ultimately had. like.
seven weeks of prep.

1394
01:11:36.168 --> 01:11:40.964
or something like that. including
these aging prosthetics and looks

1395
01:11:41.048 --> 01:11:43.258
that you and David have here.

1396
01:11:43.342 --> 01:11:47.221
and our whole team
just knocked it out of the park.

1397
01:11:47.721 --> 01:11:50.599
Normally. we would have much longer
to test these things

1398
01:11:50.682 --> 01:11:54.353
and... and they just did
such a tremendous job.

1399
01:11:54.436 --> 01:11:56.939
I mean. you got... You both look beautiful.

1400
01:11:57.022 --> 01:11:59.149
Yeah. they... That was the...
That was the challenge

1401
01:11:59.233 --> 01:12:03.028
